RAET1E


Description

Retinoic acid early transcript 1E (RAET1E). Binds and activates the KLRK1/NKG2D receptor, mediating natural killer cell cytotoxicity.


Clinical trials

NCT04107142 - Colorectal Cancer, Prostate Cancer, Sarcoma
